  },
  "CardHelpSection": {
    "ParentObjectID": "advanced_copper_tools_tea_blending_station",
    "LocalizationKey": "Advanced_Copper_Tools_TeaBlendingStation_CardHelpSection",
    "DefaultText": "<b>Slots (×6):</b> Place fresh herbs — they dry passively over time. Use 'Grind All' to mill every dried or millable item at once. <b>Water Tank:</b> Drag any container with water to add a Water Charge (up to 8). Drag an empty clay bowl to draw cold water back out. Light the stove to heat the water for tea brewing."
  },
